                              "content": "Excavation and grading for the foundation area of Building A. Includes removal of topsoil, excavation to required depth per structural drawings, and grading to achieve proper drainage slopes.\n\nKey scope items:\n• Clear and strip topsoil from foundation footprint\n• Excavate to bearing elevation (-4.5m)\n• Grade and compact subgrade to 95% Proctor\n• Install temporary dewatering if groundwater encountered\n• Stockpile suitable backfill material on-site",
